	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=260477><span id= >mjseck</span></a><br><span id=notbold>10 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p> Anyone have some tips for quad or more kiting for a 59 bard? I can fear kite NP and can twist with the best, but I cant seem to get the hang true kiting. Any tips? I have my epic so no switching instruments.<br><br>Thanks<br><br>Meter 59 Epic Bard<br>Tenzer 61/24 Necro<br>Rigby 60/6 Cleric&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
