	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=61546><span id=Sage>Slipskin</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>1154 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.69]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>The practice is called AFK training.&nbsp;&nbsp;Move bard to safe location before you leave (like the Arena off Lake Ratheater). Equip your instrument.  Start the appropriate song for that instrument.  Type /AFK Just sitting here blowing my horn, or some other appropriate message.  Walk away from the keyboard and<br><br>a) watch that movie you've been wanting to see<br><br>b) have fun with your significant other<br><br>c) clean up the house<br><br>d) go to bed<br><br>or any number of other things you need to do but were too busy feeding your EQ addiction to worry about.<br><br>You see?  Bards are the best class to play since they force you to balance game time with real life!</p>&nbsp;<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222</a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760</a></td></tr>
