	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=298861><span id= >Hellfish</span></a><br><span id=notbold>1 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Use this one:<br><br>Hotkey<br>/stopsong<br>/cast 1<br><br>That way instead of tapping once to stop then again to start a new song, you just tap once when you want to start that new song.&nbsp;&nbsp;Instead of spells directly on the hotkey bar, name the hotkeys SELO, BUFF1, BUFF2, AEDOT1, etc.<br><br>It helps quite a bit, surprisingly enough.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
