	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=173421><span id=Scholar>Quasare</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>54 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Hello, here are few answers:<br><br>_When can I solo? <br>=&gt; You can solo from lvl1 to lvl65 as a bard.<br>For the &quot;kiting&quot;, you can start it from lvl2 (AE), &quot;fear kit&quot; at lvl26, &quot;charm kit&quot; at lvl27, and &quot;chant kit&quot; from lvl30 (but better when you reach lvl46: you can twist 3 dot songs).<br><br>_When can I start to solo planes?<br>=&gt; You can solo planes at lvl46...(try PoN first with the spiders and treants), forget about old planes (Fear, Sky, Hate, PoG); you can try also PoMischief with is very nice xp (still at 65).<br><br>_Any good guides out there?<br>=&gt; EQdiva is the best of the best.<br>I did a website for bards, but it is not really &quot;up to date&quot; :p<br>www.chez.com/legacyofaggression<br><br>_Advice on pulling<br>=&gt; You have to sing the lull song on each targeted mob.<br><br>Hope this help )</p>&nbsp;<br>Valaba Noirac<br>Bard<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=150528" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=150528</a></td></tr>
